tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE urban_development_projects (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(255),
    project_location VARCHAR(255),
    land_use_before_project VARCHAR(255),
    land_use_after_project VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE urban_development_projects (
	project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	project_name VARCHAR(50),
	project_type VARCHAR(50),
	start_date DATE,
	end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE land_use_before (
	land_use_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	project_id INT,
	green_spaces_before INT,
	other_spaces_before INT,
	FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES urban_development_projects(project_id)
);

CREATE TABLE land_use_after (
	land_use_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	project_id INT,
	green_spaces_after INT,
	other_spaces_after INT,
	FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES urban_development_projects(project_id)
);

CREATE TABLE urban_development_projects (project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
project_name VARCHAR(255),
start_date DATE,
end_date DATE,
project_description TEXT);

CREATE TABLE land_use_before (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
area_id INT,
land_type VARCHAR(50),
area_covered FLOAT,
year DATE);

CREATE TABLE land_use_after (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
area_id INT,
land_type VARCHAR(50),
area_covered FLOAT,
year DATE);

CREATE TABLE green_spaces_impact (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
area_id INT,
project_id INT,
land_type VARCHAR(50),
area_covered_before FLOAT,
area_covered_after FLOAT,
impact_percentage FLOAT);

CREATE TABLE LandUseDataBefore (
    land_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT,
    land_area FLOAT,
    land_type VARCHAR(50),
    CONSTRAINT fk_project_id FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES UrbanDevelopmentProjects(project_id) 
);

CREATE TABLE LandUseDataAfter (
    land_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT,
    land_area FLOAT,
    land_type VARCHAR(50),
    CONSTRAINT fk_project_id FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES UrbanDevelopmentProjects(project_id) 
);

CREATE TABLE GreenSpacesBefore (
    green_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    land_id INT,
    green_area FLOAT,
    green_type VARCHAR(50),
    CONSTRAINT fk_land_id FOREIGN KEY (land_id) REFERENCES LandUseDataBefore(land_id) 
);

CREATE TABLE GreenSpacesAfter (
    green_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    land_id INT,
    green_area FLOAT,
    green_type VARCHAR(50),
    CONSTRAINT fk_land_id FOREIGN KEY (land_id) REFERENCES LandUseDataAfter(land_id) 
);
